Subject: Re: Windshield smearing in snow driving

In Ohio we are getting the same smearing effect because the State Highway 
crews are mixing big batches of sugar beet juice into the salt mix which 
they spray on the roads.  It is cheaper than salt or calcium chloride. 
Rain-X helped.

